%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBiden%20raised%20tariffs%20on%20China's%20green%20tech%2C%20but%20spared%20graphite%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20dominates%20global%20graphite%20supply%2C%20which%20is%20vital%20for%20EV%20batteries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESila%20CEO%20said%20the%20delay%20harms%20investment%20in%20the%20US%20battery%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20this%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-joe-biden-hikes-tariffs-on-chinese-made-evs-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiked%20tariffs%20on%20China's%3C%2Fa%3E%20massive%20green-tech%20sector%2C%20which%20includes%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20batteries%2C%20solar%20cells%2C%20and%20certain%20critical%20minerals%2C%20touting%20them%20as%20a%20way%20to%20protect%20American%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Gene%20Berdichevsky%20saw%20a%20gaping%20hole.%20The%20White%20House%20decided%20to%20delay%20by%20two%20years%20tariffs%20on%20graphite%2C%20a%20key%20metal%20in%20EV%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20that%20helps%20them%20store%20energy.%20China%20mines%20and%20processes%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20world's%20supply%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.usgs.gov%2Fperiodicals%2Fmcs2024%2Fmcs2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20federal%20US%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20our%20policy%20is%20that%20China%20is%20not%20playing%20on%20a%20level%20playing%20field%2C%20so%20we're%20going%20to%20use%20tools%20to%20level%20them%2C%20then%20we%20should%20do%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20actually%20has%20the%20outcome%20we%20want%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20to%20develop%20domestic%20battery%20supply%20chains%2C%26quot%3B%20Berdichevsky%20said%20Tuesday%20during%20dinner%20with%20reporters%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerdichevsky%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Sila%2C%20a%20next-generation%20battery%20materials%20startup%20that%20uses%20silicon%20instead%20of%20graphite.%20The%20company's%20technology%20makes%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20lighter%20than%20what's%20on%20the%20market%20today%2C%20and%20the%20firm%20says%20it%20helps%20store%2020%25%20more%20energy%2C%20or%20up%20to%20100%20extra%20miles%20for%20some%20EVs.%20Berdichevsky%2C%20an%20early%20employee%20at%20Tesla%2C%20said%20he%20saw%20a%20future%20where%20EVs%20could%20recharge%20in%2010%20minutes%2C%20which%20would%20rival%20a%20stop%20at%20the%20gas%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESila%20opened%20a%20factory%20last%20year%20in%20Moses%20Lake%2C%20Washington%2C%20with%20help%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.silanano.com%2Fpress%2Fpress-releases%2Fu-s-department-of-energy-awards-sila-100-million-to-scale-manufacturing-of-its-next-generation-anode-materials%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%24100%20million%20grant%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Energy.%20The%20company%20aims%20to%20make%20enough%20battery%20materials%20to%20power%20200%2C000%20EVs%20by%202026%2C%20and%20Mercedes-Benz%20is%20already%20a%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManufacturing%20a%20new%20technology%20in%20the%20US%20is%20challenging%20for%20a%20number%20of%20reasons.%20In%20Sila's%20case%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20scale%20big%20enough%20to%20meet%20the%20demand%20of%20large%20automakers%2C%20Berdichevsky%20said.%20That%20requires%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20to%20raise%20funds%20between%20the%20venture-capital%20and%20private-equity%20stages%20%E2%80%94%20a%20gap%20he%20described%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmissing%20middle.%26quot%3B%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20US%20is%20slow%20to%20transform%20its%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20power%20grids%20and%20EV%20charging%2C%20which%20would%20drive%20demand%20for%20homegrown%20green%20tech.%20Meanwhile%2C%20there's%20the%20risk%20that%20another%20company%20copies%20the%20technology%20and%20tries%20to%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20White%20House%20is%20sending%20a%20disappointing%20signal%20to%20Sila's%20investors%20by%20exempting%20Chinese%20graphite%20from%20tariffs%20and%20other%20policies%20designed%20to%20shift%20automakers%20away%20from%20sourcing%20batteries%20and%20critical%20minerals%20from%20China%2C%20Berdichevsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20if%20the%20White%20House%20slapped%20tariffs%20on%20graphite%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20market%20would%20react%20and%20go%2C%20'Oh%2C%20there's%20this%20new%20technology%20that%20can%20replace%20graphite%20that's%20made%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20let%20me%20go%20and%20invest%20in%20that.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20trade%20barriers%20would%20make%20EVs%20sold%20in%20the%20US%20more%20expensive%2C%20Berdichevsky%20added.%20But%20it%20would%20send%20a%20strong%20signal%20%26quot%3Bto%20get%20the%20hell%20out%20of%20Chinese%20graphite%20right%20now%2C%20not%20two%20years%20from%20now%20or%20longer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20didn't%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20But%20a%20senior%20Biden%20administration%20official%20said%20during%20a%20call%20with%20reporters%20that%20some%20tariffs%20would%20kick%20in%20in%202026%20to%20allow%20battery%20supply%20chains%20to%20transition.%20Domestic%20production%20is%20beginning%20to%20come%20online%20but%20not%20quickly%20enough%20to%20minimize%20market%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edf.org%2Fmedia%2Fanalysis-finds-us-electric-vehicle-battery-manufacturing-track-meet-demand%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%20by%20the%20Environmental%20Defense%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20enough%20US%20battery%20production%20had%20been%20announced%20to%20supply%20all%20the%20EVs%20expected%20to%20be%20sold%20in%202030.%20However%2C%20those%20batteries%20can%20still%20source%20graphite%20from%20China%20until%20at%20least%202027%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20graphite%2C%20other%20tariffs%20that%20Biden%20slapped%20on%20China's%20green%20tech%20are%20mostly%20symbolic.%20Existing%20tariffs%20already%20keep%20Chinese%20EVs%20out%20of%20the%20US%20market%2C%20while%20cheap%20solar%20panels%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-fights-back-china-cheap-solar-panels-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emainly%20arriving%20from%20Southeast%20Asia%20to%20circumvent%20trade%20barriers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20steeper%20taxes%20on%20batteries%20this%20year%20could%20affect%20US%20automakers%20such%20as%20Ford%20and%20Tesla%2C%20which%20import%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbidens-tariffs-china-green-tech-graphite-ev-batteries-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715857261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6645244b9fc063e829b1809e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbidens-tariffs-china-green-tech-graphite-ev-batteries-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CEO%20of%20Sila%2C%20a%20battery%20materials%20startup%2C%20says%20delaying%20graphite%20tariffs%20will%20slow%20investment%20in%20US%20battery%20supply%20chains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbidens-tariffs-china-green-tech-graphite-ev-batteries-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20watch%20PGA%20Championship%3A%20Live%20stream%20the%202024%20golf%20tournament%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2225