20Women%20Swati%20Maliwal%20that%20has%20put%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal-led%20party%20in%20a%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Maliwal%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20by%20Bibhav%20Kumar%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20personal%20assistant%2C%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20Monday%20morning.%20She%20is%20yet%20to%20file%20a%20complaint.%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20told%20the%20media%20that%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20%26quot%3Bmisbehaved%26quot%3B%20with%20Ms%20Maliwal%2C%20who%20went%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20to%20meet%20him.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20taken%20note%20and%20%26quot%3Bstrictest%26quot%3B%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20On%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%20assault%20case%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...If%20any%20atrocity%20happens%20to%20any%20woman%20anywhere%2C%20we%20stand%20with%20the%20woman.%20I%20always%20stand%20with%20women%20-%20irrespective%20of%20which%20party%20they%20belong%20to.%20Secondly%2C%20AAP%20will%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fw1yoAbEjGm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fw1yoAbEjGm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1791038278042554564%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20team%20comprising%20three%20IPS%20officers%20visited%20Ms%20Maliwal's%20Delhi%20residence.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20news%20agency%20ANI%20asked%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20about%20the%20matter%20concerning%20its%20ally%20AAP%2C%20she%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20two%20issues%20here.%20If%20any%20atrocity%20happens%20to%20any%20woman%20anywhere%2C%20we%20stand%20with%20the%20woman.%20I%20always%20stand%20with%20women%20-%20irrespective%20of%20which%20party%20they%20belong%20to.%20And%2C%20AAP%20will%20discuss%20it%20among%20themselves%20and%20take%20a%20decision.%20It%20is%20up%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20is%20in%20Raebareli%20to%20campaign%20for%20her%20brother%20and%20Congress%20candidate%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20the%20May%2020%20election.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20bitter%20rivals%2C%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20have%20now%20joined%20forces%20under%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20to%20take%20on%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20have%20an%20alliance%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20winning%20all%20seven%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20over%20the%20past%20two%20elections.%20The%20two%20allies%20are%2C%20however%2C%20on%20opposite%20sides%20in%20Punjab%2C%20where%20AAP%20is%20in%20power%20and%20Congress%20is%20the%20main%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20polls%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20due%20on%20May%2025%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20gone%20all-out%20against%20AAP%20in%20the%20alleged%20assault%20case.%20The%20BJP's%20charge%20also%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20release%20on%20interim%20bail%2C%20following%20which%20the%20AAP%20leader%20has%20launched%20scathing%20attacks%20on%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-avoids-questions-on-swati-maliwal-row-aap-leader-replies-5674715%5C%22%3Equestions%20on%20the%20Swati%20Maliwal%20case%20today%20at%20a%20press%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20Lucknow.%20When%20a%20journalist%20asked%20him%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20there%20are%20more%20important%20issues%20to%20be%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20seated%20next%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20responded%20to%20the%20question.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20country%20is%20upset%20that%20a%20Kargil%20hero's%20wife%20was%20stripped%20and%20paraded%20in%20Manipur%2C%20scores%20of%20women%20were%20tortured%2C%20but%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20silent.%20Thousands%20of%20women%20were%20raped%20by%20(JDS%20MP)%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20seeks%20votes%20for%20him.%20The%20BJP%20helps%20him%20flee%20the%20country.%20When%20our%20wrestler%20daughters%20were%20fighting%20for%20justice%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%2C%20it%20was%20Swati%20Maliwal%2C%20then%20Chairperson%20of%20(Delhi)%20Women's%20Commission%2C%20who%20went%20to%20support%20them%20and%20was%20dragged%20and%20beaten%20by%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20is%20a%20family.%20%26quot%3BThe%20party%20has%20made%20its%20stance%20clear%2C%20and%20I%20want%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20BJP%20to%20respond%20to%20all%20the%20issues%20I%20have%20raised.%20Please%20don't%20play%20political%20games%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20corner%20AAP%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20questioned%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20silence%20on%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20party%2C%20but%20BJP%20is%20fighting%20to%20ensure%20that%20she%20gets%20justice.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20should%20answer%2C%20if%20you%20are%20a%20coward%20CM%20and%20cannot%20speak%20a%20single%20word%2C%20then%20you%20should%20resign%20because%20the%20women%20of%20the%20country%20are%20angry%20and%20feeling%20insulted%20and%20only%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20party%20spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715856600000%2