ccident%20but%20also%20to%20the%20nature%20and%20extent%20of%20the%20claimant's%20injuries%20on%20his%20employment%20prospects%20and%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20insolvency%20of%20his%20company%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20company's%20past%20and%20future%20performance.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20due%20to%20take%20place%20over%20four%20days%20in%20Central%20London%20County%20Court%2C%20medical%20professionals%2C%20including%20neurologists%20and%20orthopaedic%20surgeons%2C%20will%20testify.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715854980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ff6i0qeug_british-airways_625x300_16_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fswiss-businessman-sues-british-airways-for-rs-52-crore-after-slipping-on-liquor-says-he-suffered-brain-injury-5676407%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20fall%20resulted%20in%20headaches%2C%20forgetfulness%2C%20and%20concentration%20issues%20that%20impacted%20his%20ability%20to%20work%2C%20ultimately%20causing%20his%20office%20supplies%20company%20to%20shut%20down.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fswiss-businessman-sues-british-airways-for-rs-52-crore-after-slipping-on-liquor-says-he-suffered-brain-injury-5676407%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fswiss-businessman-sues-british-airways-for-rs-52-crore-after-slipping-on-liquor-says-he-suffered-brain-injury-5676407%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fswiss-businessman-sues-british-airways-for-rs-52-crore-after-slipping-on-liquor-says-he-suffered-brain-injury-5676407%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netgear%20explores%20possibility%20of%20building%20manufacturing%20facilities%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17158547