0%E2%80%9Chigh%20key%20super%20sweet%C2%A0and%C2%A0I'd%C2%A0never%20wanna%20disrespect%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%C2%A0latest%20iPad%20Pro%20advertisement%20showed%20the%C2%A0tablet's%C2%A0capabilities%2C%20including%20watching%20TV%20shows%2C%20listening%20to%20music%2C%20and%20playing%20video%20games%2C%20while%20focussing%20on%20its%20slim%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ad%20showed%20a%20visual%20theme%2C%20but%20controversy%20sparked%20when%20the%20ad%20showed%20a%20hydraulic%20press%20destroying%20creative%20instruments%20and%20devices%2C%20which%20many%20found%20insensitive%20and%20disrespectful.%20Critics%20argued%20that%20in%20this%20instance%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20has%20damaged%20its%20reputation%2C%20with%20some%20complaining%20that%20the%20ad%20suggests%20technology%20stifles%20creativity%20instead%20of%20fostering%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FntjkwIXWtrc%3Fsi%3DluApBNa1gIEnDfHc%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWidespread%20criticism%20followed%2C%20with%20Apple%20accused%20of%20being%C2%A0%26quot%3Btone%20deaf%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20faced%20criticism%20for%20his%20post%20on%C2%A0X%C2%A0where%20he%20encouraged%20people%20to%C2%A0%26quot%3Bimagine%20all%20the%20things%C2%A0it'll%C2%A0be%20used%C2%A0to%20create.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20company%20deleted%20the%20ad%20from%20airwaves%20and%C2%A0issued%20an%20apology.%20Tor%20Myhren%2C%C2%A0Apple's%C2%A0VP%20of%20marketing%20communications%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cthey%20missed%20the%20mark%E2%80%9D%C2%A0with%20the%20controversial%20video.%C2%A0%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%C2%A0to%20always%20celebrate%C2%A0the%20myriad%20of%20ways%20users%20