hen%20disguise%20the%20source%20of%20those%20funds%20(money%20laundering).%20Anton%20Peraire-Bueno%20was%20apprehended%20in%20Boston%2C%20while%20James%20Peraire-Bueno%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Peraire-Bueno%20brothers%20haven't%20commented%20on%20the%20charges%20yet.%20Prosecutors%20claim%20their%20MIT%20education%20in%20computer%20science%20and%20math%20provided%20the%20foundation%20for%20their%20alleged%20crime.%20The%20indictment%20accuses%20them%20of%20spending%20months%20devising%20a%20plan%20to%20exploit%20vulnerabilities%20in%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%2C%20the%20system%20that%20verifies%20and%20records%20cryptocurrency%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20allege%20the%20brothers%20found%20a%20loophole%20in%20a%20program%20called%20MEV-boost%2C%20commonly%20used%20by%20Ethereum%20validators%20to%20verify%20transactions.%20By%20exploiting%20this%20weakness%2C%20they%20supposedly%20manipulated%20the%20system%20and%20stole%20the%20cryptocurrency.%20%C2%A0After%20the%20heist%2C%20instead%20of%20returning%20the%20funds%2C%20the%20brothers%20allegedly%20took%20steps%20to%20conceal%20the%20stolen%20money%20through%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20each%20face%20over%2020%20years%20in%20prison%20if%20found%20guilty%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-69018575%5C%22%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715848080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fpds3t6d8_crypto_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmit-graduates-arrested-for-stealing-25-million-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds-5675685%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anton%20and%20James%20Peraire-Bueno%2C%20aged%2024%20and%2028%20respectively%2C%20allegedly%20manipulated%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%20in%20a%20mere%2012%20seconds%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmit-graduates-arrested-for-stealing-25-million-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds-5675685%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmit-graduates-arrested-for-stealing-25-million-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds-5675685%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmit-graduates-arrested-for-stealing-25-million-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds-5675685%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hardik%20Picked%20For%20T20%20WC%20'Under%20Pressure'%3B%20Rohit-Agarkar%20Against%20It%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20rumours%20of%20a%20possible%20rift%20between%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20ever%20since%20the%20latter%20was%20appointed%20captain%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024.%20Hardik%20had%20replaced%20Rohit%20as%20MI%20captain%20after%20rejoining%20the%20franchise%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%20during%20the%20trade%20window.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20say%20that%20the%20move%20has%20backfired%20as%20MI%20are%20already%20out%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs%20contention.%20Also%2C%20Hardik's%20performance%20this%20season%20has%20been%20mediocre%20to%20say%20the%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2013%20games%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20200%20runs%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20144.93%2C%20while%20also%20taking%2011%20wickets%20in%2013%20matches%20at%20an%20economy%20of%2010.59.%20Most%20of%20his%20good%20bowling%20performances%20have%20come%20in%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hardik%20was%20still%20picked%20by%20the%20selectors%20in%20the%2015-man%20squad%20for%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Americas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20had%20recently%20claimed%20that%20neither%20Rohit%20nor%20the%20selection%20committee%2C%20led%20by%20former%20India%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajit%20Agarkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F100-ajit-agarkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjit%20Agarkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20selecting%20Hardik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20report%20said%20that%20Hardik%20was%20picked%20in%20the%20team%20under%20'pressure'.%20The%20report%20did%20not%20mention%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20situational%20pressure%20(as%20he%20is%20India's%20top%20fast%20bowling%20allrounder)%20or%20a%20pressure%20from%20some%20quarters.%20The%20report%20also%20attributed%20sources%20as%20saying%20that%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20%2C%20BCCI%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20and%20some%20selectors%20were%20against%20Pandya's%20selection%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20team%2C%20during%20the%20selection%20meeting%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabhishereporter%2Fstatus%2F1789484622436614531%5C%22%3EDainik%20Jagran%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20added%20that%20Rohit%20might%20retire%20from%20the%20T20%20format%20after%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Hardik's%20place%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20is%20not%20a%20surity.%20And%20even%20if%20he%20plays%2C%20he%20might%20not%20feature%20in%20all%20of%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Rohit%20and%20Agarkar%20attended%20the%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%20selection%2C%20the%20chief%20selector%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Hardik%20in%20the%20roster%20despite%20his%20poor%20form.%20In%20response%2C%20Agarkar%20explained%20how%20the%20selection%20committee%20didn't%20have%20a%20choice%20as%20there's%20no%20like-for-like%20replacement%20for%20Hardik%20available%20from%20the%20talent%20pool%20that%20exists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20play%20three%20of%20their%20four%20Group%20A%20matches%20in%20New%20York%20including%20the%20highly-anticipated%20clash%20with%20Pakistan%20on%20June%209.%20Their%20fourth%20fixture%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Florida%2C%20against%20Canada%20on%20June%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715848020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftgmpf03g_rohit-sharma-ajit-agarkar-afp_625x300_07_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fhardik-pandya-picked-for-t20-wc-under-pressure-rohit-sharma-ajit-agarkar-against-it-report-5675660%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20have%20been%20rumours%20of%20a%20possible%20rift%20between%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20ever%20since%20the%20latter%20was%20appointed%20captain%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fhardik-pandya-picked-for-t20-wc-under-pressure-rohit-sharma-ajit-agarkar-against-it-report-5675660%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fhardik-pandya-picked-for-t20-wc-under-pressure-rohit-sharma-ajit-agarkar-against-it-report-5675660%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fhardik-pandya-picked-for-t20-wc-under-pressure-rohit-sharma-ajit-agarkar-against-it-report-5675660%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ED%20can't%20arrest%20after%20special%20court%20takes%20cognizance%20of%20PMLA%20complaint%3A%20SC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715848020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110172857%2Cimgsize-1466698.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fed-cant-arrest-after-special-court-takes-cognizance-of-pmla-complaint-supreme-court%2Farticleshow%2F110172775.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20held%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20cannot%20arrest%20an%20accused%20person%20after%20the%20special%20court%20has%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20the%20complaint.%20A%20bench%20of%20justices%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20if%20ED%20requires%20custody%2C%20then%20the%20probe%20agency%20can%20move%20the%20application%20before%20the%20concerned%20court%20and%20thereafter%2C%20the%20court%20can%20only%20grant%20custody%20once%20satisfied%20with%20the%20reasons%20that%20custodial%20interrogation%20is%20required.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woo-seok%20was%20NOT%20the%20first%20choice%20for%20Lovely%20Runner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715847843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110172702%2Cimgsize-26680.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fbyun-woo-seok-was-not-the-first-choice-for-lovely-runner-script-was-offered-to-other-actors-rejected%2Farticleshow%2F110172711.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110172711.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EByun%20Woo-seok%2C%20of%20'Lovely%20Runner'%2C%20joined%20'You%20Quiz%20on%20the%20Block'%20with%20Yoo%20Jae-suk.%20Shared%20insights%20about%20the%20drama%2C%20co-star%20Kim%20Hye-yoon%2C%20and%20upcoming%20episode%20details.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fbyun-woo-seok-was-not-the-first-choice-for-lovely-runner-script-was-offered-to-other-actors-rejected%2Farticleshow%2F110172711.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BProbe%20Agency%20Can't%20Arrest%20Accused%20If...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court's%20Big%20Ruling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20ruling%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20curtailed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fenforcement-directorate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fa%3E's%20power%20to%20arrest%20an%20accused%20-%20under%20Section%2019%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20or%20PMLA%20-%20if%20the%20accused%20appears%20as%20summoned%20by%20a%20special%20court%20that%20has%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20cases%20the%20agency%20must%20first%20seek%20that%20court's%20nod%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20cognisance%20is%20taken%20of%20the%20offence...%20the%20ED%20and%20its%20officers%20are%20powerless%20to%20exercise%20powers%20under%20Section%2019%20to%20arrest%20the%20person%20shown%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2019%20of%20the%20PMLA%20allows%20ED%20officers%20to%20arrest%20an%20individual%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20basis%20of%20material%20in%20possession%20(and)%20reason%20to%20believe%20(to%20be%20recorded%20in%20writing)%20that%20the%20person%20is%20guilty...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20agency%20must%20inform%20the%20individual%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20may%20be%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20grounds%20for%20the%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%20in%20cases%20where%20an%20accused%20was%20not%20arrested%20till%20the%20time%20the%20ED%20filed%20its%20complaint%2C%20they%20could%20not%20be%20arrested%20afterwards.%20The%20special%20court%20must%20first%20issue%20a%20summons%20and%2C%20if%20the%20accused%20duly%20answers%20that%20summons%2C%20they%20could%20not%20been%20seen%20as%20being%20'in%20custody'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20ED%20wants%20custody%20of%20(an)%20accused%20after%20the%20person%20(answers%20a%20special%20court's)%20summons%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20apply%20to%20the%20special%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhayan%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20custody%20could%20only%20be%20granted%20if%20that%20court%20believes%20custodial%20interrogation%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20arrest%20warrant%20-%20under%20Section%2070%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20-%20can%20only%20be%20issued%20if%20the%20accused%20failed%20to%20answer%20the%20summons%2C%20and%2C%20in%20the%20first%20instance%2C%20this%20must%20be%20a%20bailable%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-today-enforcement-directorate-cant-keep-filing-chargesheets-to-keep-people-in-jail-observes-top-court-5274968%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCan't%20Keep%20Filing%20Chargesheets%20To%20Keep%20People%20In%20Jail%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20ruling%20-%20one%20seen%20as%20emphasising%20protection%20offered%20from%20arbitrary%20arrest%20by%20the%20central%20agency%20-%20the%20top%20court%20also%20said%20accused%20individuals%20not%20arrested%20before%20answering%20a%20court%20summons%20-%20need%20satisfy%20the%20stringent%20'twin%20test'%20for%20bail%20as%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20PMLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'twin%20test'%20states%20bail%20will%20only%20be%20given%20to%20money%20laundering%20accused%20if%20the%20court%20is%20satisfied%20the%20individual%20is%20not%20guilty%20and%20if%20they%20are%20unlikely%20to%20commit%20crimes%2C%20including%20similar%20offences%2C%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20specific%20background%20to%20this%20ruling%20is%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20in%20which%20the%20accused%20had%20appeared%20before%20a%20special%20court%20as%20summoned.%20The%20question%20then%20was%20if%20the%20accused%20had%20to%20meet%20the%20'twin%20test'%20for%20grant%20of%20bail%20if%20the%20special%20court%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20offence%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20earlier%20reserved%20its%20judgement%20on%20April%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-hindustan-times-interview-enforcement-directorate-only-3-of-cases-pms-sharp-jab-to-oppositions-probe-agency-claims-5425106%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOnly%203%25%20Of%20Cases...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM's%20Jab%20To%20Opposition's%20Probe%20Agency%20Claims%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20landmark%20ruling%20comes%20two%20months%20after%20the%20top%20court%20dismissed%20a%20petition%20seeking%20review%20of%20an%20earlier%20verdict%20that%20said%20the%20ED%20is%20required%20to%20furnish%20grounds%20of%20arrest%20to%20an%20accused%20in%20writing%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20exception%26quot%3B%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20error%20in%20its%20judgement%20warranting%20reconsideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20court%20had%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Bmere%20non-cooperation%20of%20a%20witness%2C%20in%20response%20to%20summons%20issued%20under%20Section%2050%2C%20will%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20render%20him%2Fher%20liable%20to%20arrest%20under%20Section%2019%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchann