20%E2%80%98foodpharmer%E2%80%99%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20year%2C%20this%2032-year-old%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20charge%20in%20promoting%20health%20literacy%20and%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%20before%20making%20purchases.%20Through%20his%20Instagram%20page%2C%20he%20has%20gathered%20a%20following%20of%20over%202.2%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20left%20behind%20a%20lucrative%20Rs%202%20crore%20job%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20this%20certified%20health%20coach%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20spark%20a%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20revolution%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndians%20are%20educated%20but%20not%20health%20literate.%20I%E2%80%99m%20therefore%20focusing%20on%20health%20literacy%2C%20with%20my%20major%20target%20being%20children.%20You%20should%20develop%20healthy%20habits%20in%20children%20from%20day%20one%20and%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20junk%20to%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20developing%20health%20issues%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHolding%20large%20FMCG%20conglomerates%20accountable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%2090s%20Kolkata%2C%20Revant%20had%20a%20regular%20childhood%2C%20which%20included%20biscuits%2C%20packaged%20foods%2C%20and%20drinks%20like%20Bournvita.%20The%20young%20boy%20was%20then%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20the%20food%20he%20consumed%2C%20like%20millions%20of%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Revant%20wants%20Indians%20to%20learn%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the