sed%20dessert%3C%2Fa%3E.%20FDA%20too%2C%20mandates%20that%20a%20true%20ice%20cream%20must%20have%20at%20least%2010%20percent%20milk%20in%20it.%20So%20if%20the%20label%20does%20say%20milk%2C%20it%20is%20NOT%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20frozen%20desserts%20may%20taste%20and%20feel%20similar%20to%20ice%20creams%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20know%20that%20frozen%20desserts%20have%20a%20higher%20fat%20content.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20bad%20cholesterol%2C%20and%20cause%20heart%20diseases.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHealthSite.com%20report%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(hydrogenated%20oils)%20are%20banned%20for%20US%20foods%2C%20with%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20calling%20for%20a%20total%20ban%20worldwide%20in%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20you%20know%20how%20to%20check%20if%20your%20ice%20cream%20is%20fake%2C%20make%20it%20a%20thumb%20rule%20to%20check%20the%20ingredient%20list%20before%20indulging%20in%20your%20favourite%20summer%20staple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715610434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349789%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Frozen%20desserts%20are%20masquerading%20as%20ice%20creams%20in%20the%20market.%20How%20do%20you%20differentiate%20between%20them%3F%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20simple%20steps%20to%20identify%20real%20ice%20creams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349789%2Fhow-to-identity-real-ice-cream-vs-frozen-dessert-fssai-guidelines-read-label%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IFS%20Officer%20Is%20On%20a%20Mission%20to%20Save%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Endangered%20Plants%3B%20What%20Makes%20them%20Special%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20dusk%20sets%2C%20anyone%20who%20stops%20by%20the%20research%20wing%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20in%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Haldwani%20looking%20for%20IFS%20officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20him%20there.%20Instead%2C%20the%20officer%20can%20be%20found%20promenading%20through%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20campus%20which%20teems%20with%20abundant%20flowering%20plants%20and%20fruit%20trees.%20The%20sight%20of%20a%20glorious%20green%20carpet%20thriving%20at%20a%20height%20of%20300%20ft%20above%20sea%20level%20is%20baffling.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F163949%2Fjakkur-bengaluru-lake-pollution-cleaning-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especies%20of%20flora%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20you%20think%20reside%20within%20this%2025-acre%20land%3F%20Take%20a%20guess.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20850%20species%20and%20counting%2C%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20Chaturvedi.%20In%20this%20forest-like%20ecosystem%20that%20he%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20few%20years%20cultivating%2C%20bamboo%20and%20cactus%20befriend%20each%20other%2C%20while%20crickets%2C%20butterflies%20and%20insects%20stop%20by%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20to%20the%20honeysuckle.%20The%20air%20is%20crisp%20and%20the%20walk%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20Chaturvedi%2C%20who%20pauses%20to%20put%20his%20experience%20into%20words%3B%20then%20proceeds%20to%20say%20that%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20justice.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20most%20taken%20aback%20by%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20optimistic%20view%20are%20the%20naysayers%20who%20were%20convinced%20that%20this%20particular%20posting%20in%20the%20highlands%20of%20Uttarakhand%20would%20be%20a%20test%20of%20the%20IFS%20officer%E2%80%99s%20patience.%20Their%20discouragement%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20of%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20predecessors%20had%20detested%20being%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20god-forsaken%20area%2C%20made%20the%20officer%20sceptical.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302635%2Fladakh-ministry-of-education-score-new-heights-role-of-dedicated-teachers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20harsh%20terrain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20remoteness%20of%20the%20place%2C%20did%20nothing%20to%20ease%20his%20woes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20since%20he%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20conservator%20of%20forest%20research%20(Chaturvedi%20was%20promoted%20to%20head%20of%20the%20wing%20in%202020)%2C%20this%20terrain%20evolved%20into%20a%20blessing.%20As%20Chaturvedi%20and%20his%20team%20discovered%2C%20not%20only%20was%20it%20a%20favourable%20home%20for%20Nainital%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98miracle%20plant%E2%80%99%20Patwa%2C%20but%20also%20a%20host%20of%20other%20plant%20species%20that%20are%20in%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20red%20list%20and%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%98threatened%E2%80%99%20by%20Uttarakhand%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20has%20been%20working%20closely%20to%20conserve%20plant%20habitats%20and%20protect%20them%20from%20illegal%20trade.%20They%20are%20also%20innovating%20ways%20to%20grow%20them%20in%20their%20natural%20habitats%20and%20in%20their%20research%20centres%20as%20well.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20scale%20these%20plant%20populations%20at%20their%20original%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IFS%20Officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20has%20dedicated%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20to%20conserving%20endemic%20plant%20species%20in%20Nainital%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%