-349433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Tree%20Fern%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20species%20and%20was%20once%20the%20food%20of%20dinosaurs%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chaturvedi%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20job%20is%20tough%2C%20Chaturvedi%20has%20a%20stellar%20team%20backing%20him.%20One%20of%20his%20junior%20research%20fellows%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbrilliant%20minds%E2%80%9D%2C%20Manoj%20Singh%2C%20shares%20the%20intricate%20process%20they%20follow%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276600%2Fkerala-man-converts-rubber-plantation-into-mini-forest-medicinal-fruit-plants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econserve%20these%20plant%20species%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20identify%20the%20plants%20based%20on%20their%20family%20and%20genus%2C%20then%20proceed%20to%20collect%20their%20specimens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20factors%20play%20spoilsport%20to%20this%20%E2%80%94%20illegal%20trade%2C%20growth%20of%20invasive%20species%2C%20and%20wildlife%20feasting%20on%20the%20fallen%20fruits%20and%20seeds.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20birds%20eat%20these%20seeds%20and%20fruits%2C%20it%20disturbs%20the%20natural%20regeneration%20of%20the%20plant.%20There%20is%20no%20chance%20of%20a%20new%20crop.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20and%20Chaturvedi%20lead%20the%20team%20to%20collect%20these%20fruits%20and%20seeds%20and%20take%20them%20back%20to%20the%20centre%20where%20they%20conduct%20experiments%20to%20cultivate%20these%20plants%20through%20vegetative%20propagation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20terrain%2C%20weather%20and%20climate%20are%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CEspecially%20when%2C%20after%20restoration%2C%20we%20proceed%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A