0%99ll%20see%20an%20apple%20farmer%20every%20day%20in%20the%20field%2C%20come%20what%20may%20%E2%80%94%20pest%20attacks%2C%20hailstorms%2C%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20and%20snow.%20They%20nurture%20and%20protect%20them%20like%20a%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20farmer%20himself%2C%20Ashish%20decided%20it%20was%20high%20time%20to%20redirect%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20gold%20in%20them%20thar%20hills%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Ashish%20launched%20an%20online%20platform%20%E2%80%98Kayang%E2%80%99%20to%20end%20the%20woes%20of%20farmers%20and%20bring%20them%20profits%20directly%20from%20end-consumers.%20The%20apples%20are%20directly%20sourced%20from%20small%20farmers.%20After%20sorting%2C%20grading%2C%20and%20packaging%2C%20the%20company%20transports%20them%20to%20consumers%20across%20India.%20For%20this%2C%20a%20team%20of%20300%20people%20is%20employed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-3-1715174431.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashish's%20startup%20supplies%20Kinnauri%20apples%20from%20farmers%20to%20customers%20directly%20%E2%80%94%20saving%20them%20from%20a%20vicious%20circle%20of%20middlemen.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-3-1715174431.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-3-1715174431-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-3-1715174431-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-3-1715174431-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FK